narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Much harder than L1 Spanish, but more of the same with grammar, compositions, listening exams, etc.
a lot to learn in a little time, but you'll have fun along the way. Work hard and you'll do well. Yes, recommended.
I would recommend this class to another student. It's hard but if you get a good teacher it can be a good learning experience.
You are gonna take it if you took 110 so what I say here won't matter. Just take it with Janelle if she is teaching again!
Yes I would recommend it to another student.
